title: United Kingdom Imports - Soaps,Organic Agents, Lubricating, Waxes Prepared
description: Imports - Soaps,Organic Agents, Lubricating, Waxes Prepared in the United Kingdom decreased to 209.50 GBP Million in September from 244.66 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports - Soaps,Organic Agents, Lubricating, Waxes in the United Kingdom averaged 119.15 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 244.66 GBP Million in August of 2022 and a record low of 45.01 GBP Million in December of 2000. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Soaps,organic Agents, Lubricating, Wax.
